data.description: Welcome to your stunning lakeside retreat! This beautifully updated home on Swan Lake offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and serene natural surroundings. Step inside to discover a remodeled kitchen, new flooring throughout, and a brand-new roof, ensuring years of worry-free living.  Whether you're hosting a dinner party or enjoying a quiet morning coffee, this kitchen is sure to inspire. Indulge in the comfort of the updated bathroom, featuring a new vanity that adds a touch of elegance to your daily routine. With modern fixtures and thoughtful design, this space is both functional and inviting. Don't miss your opportunity to enjoy the sunroom that overlooks the park-like backyard of this lakeside home. Schedule your showing today and make your dreams of lakefront living a reality!
